<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA521_04_IH_0005</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="../../common_practice/js/ema521_01_02_ih.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema521_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema521_04_ih_0005">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="5" class="is_star" lang="y">은서네 모둠의 훌라후프 돌리기 기록과 기록별 받는 상을 나타낸 표입니다. 은상을 받는 학생의 이름을 모두 골라 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents">
        <div class="l_layout">
          <div class="l_left">
            <h4 class="has_bg" lang="y">학생별 훌라후프 돌리기 기록</h4>
            <div class="flex gap_30">
              <div class="table_wrap">
                <table>
                  <colgroup>
                    <col />
                    <col />
                  </colgroup>
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      <th lang="y" scope="col">이름</th>
                      <th lang="y" scope="col">기록(초)</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <th lang="y" scope="row">은서</th>
                      <td lang="y">45</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <th lang="y" scope="row">소정</th>
                      <td lang="y">50</td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
              <div class="table_wrap">
                <table>
                  <colgroup>
                    <col />
                    <col />
                  </colgroup>
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      <th lang="y" scope="col">이름</th>
                      <th lang="y" scope="col">기록(초)</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <th lang="y" scope="row">지효</th>
                      <td lang="y">45</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <th lang="y" scope="row">재한</th>
                      <td lang="y">50</td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <div>
                <button type="button" data-answer-single="false" class="button1"></button>
                <button type="button" data-answer-single="false" class="button2"></button>
                <button type="button" data-answer-single="true" class="button3"></button>
                <button type="button" data-answer-single="true" class="button4"></button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="l_right">
            <h4 class="has_bg" lang="y">훌라우프 돌리기 기록별 받는 상</h4>
            <div class="table_wrap">
              <table>
                <colgroup>
                  <col />
                  <col />
                </colgroup>
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th lang="y" scope="col">기록(초)</th>
                    <th lang="y" scope="col">상</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr>
                    <th lang="y" scope="row">55 초과</th>
                    <td lang="y">금상</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th lang="y" scope="row">45 초과 55 이하</th>
                    <td lang="y">은상</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th lang="y" scope="row">35 초과 45 이하</th>
                    <td lang="y">동상</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">훌라후프 돌리기 기록이 45초 초과 55초 이하일 때 은상을 받을 수 있으므로 은상을 받는 학생은 기록이 50초인 소정이와 55초인 재한입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <!-- <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button> -->
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
